and would make good money.

299
00:18:07,532 --> 00:18:08,572
Also, the one who

300
00:18:09,132 --> 00:18:10,893
split orders with us, Liu Jingcai.

301
00:18:11,013 --> 00:18:11,532
Liu Jingcai.

302
00:18:11,612 --> 00:18:12,893
- He doesn't need money now.
- Right.

303
00:18:12,973 --> 00:18:14,612
He had outstanding entry at my place.

304
00:18:14,612 --> 00:18:15,453
At least, it was...

305
00:18:15,453 --> 00:18:16,453
Aunties and uncles,

306
00:18:16,453 --> 00:18:18,052
get all the money over here.

307
00:18:18,213 --> 00:18:18,933
Who hasn't?

308
00:18:18,973 --> 00:18:20,812
I've borrowed
from every relative possible.

309
00:18:21,132 --> 00:18:22,733
If we can get this done

310
00:18:22,933 --> 00:18:24,973
and pay before the cadres
in the county...

311
00:18:25,413 --> 00:18:26,852
Get that certificate approved.

312
00:18:27,092 --> 00:18:28,253
Not sure about the plan.

313
00:18:28,253 --> 00:18:30,493
