343
00:20:37,612 --> 00:20:39,653
We strongly condemn Zheng Decheng.

344
00:20:40,213 --> 00:20:41,852
We demand he be punished.

345
00:20:49,653 --> 00:20:51,013
Our original intention

346
00:20:51,733 --> 00:20:52,888
is that we are all actually

347
