355
00:21:19,453 --> 00:21:21,132
He signed it,
but didn't want to admit it.

356
00:21:21,493 --> 00:21:23,532
He wanted to eat it.
He swallowed it whole.

357
00:21:23,812 --> 00:21:25,852
I snatched this from his mouth.

358
00:21:26,413 --> 00:21:27,896
You tell me. As a leader,

359
00:21:28,152 --> 00:21:29,733
he signed it, but now he's backing out.

360
00:21:29,893 --> 00:21:32,052
Moreover,
after our communication failed,

361
00:21:32,332 --> 00:21:35,092
he gave that road
to someone else overnight!

362
00:21:35,893 --> 00:21:38,092
What kind of behavior is this?
What kind...

363
00:21:39,693 --> 00:21:41,173
What kind of behavior is this?

364
00:21:41,653 --> 00:21:42,232
Mr. Zhao,

365
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,812
