He must be severely punished.

367
00:21:48,173 --> 00:21:49,653
That's right. How could he do this?

368
00:21:50,132 --> 00:21:51,733
He can't take Binhai Road back!

369
00:21:51,733 --> 00:21:52,253
That's right.

370
00:21:52,292 --> 00:21:53,453
He must be severely punished.

371
00:21:53,493 --> 00:21:54,372
Severely punished.

372
00:21:54,413 --> 00:21:55,292
He can't take it back.

373
00:21:56,572 --> 00:21:57,693
- Right.
- Absolutely cannot let this happen.

374
00:21:58,332 --> 00:22:00,653
The news spreads really fast.

375
00:22:02,772 --> 00:22:03,532
Regret it now?

376
00:22:04,532 --> 00:22:05,372
What do you think?

377
00:22:08,852 --> 00:22:09,693
Go back and wait.

378
00:22:24,612 --> 00:22:26,612
You two go wait
in the conference room downstairs.

379
00:22:37,132 --> 00:22:38,332
(Petition)
Look at your achievements.

380
00:22:40,413 --> 00:22:41,624
Over 1,000 people accused you.

381
00:22:42,693 --> 00:22:43,413
And this.

382
00:22:45,292 --> 00:22:46,332
You bit this, didn't you?

383
00:22:47,372 --> 00:22:50,013
It was snatched from your mouth.
She said you ate it.

384
00:22:50,612 --> 00:22:52,532
I find this ridiculous, you know?

385
00:22:55,292 --> 00:22:56,253
Well done, Li.

386
00:22:57,052 --> 00:22:58,493
You just acted before reporting.

387
00:22:59,893 --> 00:23:01,812
You took the money,
completed the procedures.

388
00:23:02,372 --> 00:23:04,052
and rushed here overnight
like a heroine.

389
00:23:04,532 --> 00:23:06,413
You think that way I won't punish you?

390
00:23:06,973 --> 00:23:09,332
Mr. Zhao, the Binhai Road incident

391
00:23:09,493 --> 00:23:11,013
is indeed our mistake.

392
00:23:11,332 --> 00:23:12,572
We should be punished.

393
00:23:13,612 --> 00:23:15,372
(Conference Room)
But the people of Yuehai

394
00:23:15,653 --> 00:23:17,772
have nothing to do with this.

395
00:23:18,213 --> 00:23:20,693
Could you first help us coordinate

396
00:23:21,332 --> 00:23:22,933
to restore the electricity in Yuehai?

397
00:23:23,733 --> 00:23:24,173
Right.

398
00:23:26,612 --> 00:23:29,532
I told the Power Supply Bureau
to restore production electricity first,

399
00:23:30,292 --> 00:23:31,736
and then the domestic electricity.

400
00:23:31,933 --> 00:23:32,812
Hurry back to Yuehai.

401
00:23:33,653 --> 00:23:35,013
Calm down the people's emotions.

402
00:23:36,893 --> 00:23:38,453
But you, Zheng Decheng.

403
00:23:39,292 --> 00:23:40,253
As the Secretary,

404
00:23:40,413 --> 00:23:42,653
you have indeed hurt
the cadres' feelings.

405
00:23:42,973 --> 00:23:43,612
Do you admit it?

406
00:23:43,852 --> 00:23:44,453
I admit it.

407
00:23:44,733 --> 00:23:46,132
I'm giving you a warning this time.

408
00:23:47,772 --> 00:23:48,173
Okay.

409
00:23:49,052 --> 00:23:50,013
Teach you a lesson.

410
00:23:50,372 --> 00:23:52,602
Remember to clarify the situation first

411
00:23:52,664 --> 00:23:54,052
- before deciding next time.
- I got it.

412
00:23:54,532 --> 00:23:55,064
Moreover,

413
00:23:55,384 --> 00:23:58,213
as Yuehai's leader,
you must take responsibility.

414
00:23:58,532 --> 00:23:59,893
Tomorrow morning at 9 AM,

415
00:24:00,253 --> 00:24:01,532
come to the county government.

416
00:24:01,772 --> 00:24:02,912
Apologize to all the cadres

417
00:24:03,192 --> 00:24:05,493
for the personal debt you owe.

418
00:24:07,413 --> 00:24:07,973
Okay.

419
00:24:10,213 --> 00:24:12,653
Mr. Zhao, I arranged for the cadres
to move to Yuehai

420
00:24:12,973 --> 00:24:14,292
to settle down initially.

421
00:24:14,733 --> 00:24:17,413
I am responsible for this
in the first place.

422
00:24:19,013 --> 00:24:19,973
If there's punishment

423
00:24:21,213 --> 00:24:24,052
or an apology required,
I'll bear it as well.

424
00:24:25,493 --> 00:24:26,933
Li, I haven't criticized you yet.

425
00:24:27,532 --> 00:24:28,612
You come to take the blame?

426
00:24:28,933 --> 00:24:30,493
Tell me, what was the task I gave you?

427
00:24:30,772 --> 00:24:32,413
It was when Zheng Decheng messes around,

428
00:24:32,493 --> 00:24:33,292
you hold him back.

429
00:24:34,413 --> 00:24:35,132
What now?

430
00:24:35,693 --> 00:24:37,332
You betrayed the trust placed in you.

431
00:24:40,213 --> 00:24:41,453
I'll get back to you later.

432
00:24:42,372 --> 00:24:43,413
In the town government,

433
00:24:44,013 --> 00:24:45,893
someone has to be responsible
for production.

434
00:24:46,253 --> 00:24:47,173
Get back immediately.

435
00:24:47,733 --> 00:24:48,733
Resume work.

436
00:24:49,612 --> 00:24:51,092
Ensure Yuehai operates normally.

437
00:24:52,052 --> 00:24:52,413
Okay.

438
00:24:52,572 --> 00:24:53,173
Okay.

439
00:25:05,532 --> 00:25:06,968
Zheng Decheng, where are you going?

440
00:25:07,893 --> 00:25:09,372
How dare you leave?

441
00:25:09,733 --> 00:25:11,893
Listen, you're not going anywhere today.

442
00:25:12,092 --> 00:25:13,132
You'll stay put here.

443
00:25:13,528 --> 00:25:14,322
(Conference Room)

444
00:25:14,332 --> 00:25:16,693
Think hard about how you'll face
the cadres tomorrow.

445
00:25:18,772 --> 00:25:19,864
Write an apology letter.

446
00:25:20,612 --> 00:25:23,132
Write what you truly think.
Show some sincerity.

447
00:25:23,612 --> 00:25:24,653
Do I make myself clear?

448
00:25:25,213 --> 00:25:25,973
Yes.

449
00:25:27,493 --> 00:25:28,253
Then go write it.

450
00:25:28,893 --> 00:25:29,332
Okay.

451
00:25:30,052 --> 00:25:30,532
Well...

452
00:25:32,653 --> 00:25:33,413
Make it profound.

453
00:25:33,933 --> 00:25:34,733
Yes, got it.

454
00:25:47,132 --> 00:25:47,772
Mr. Zhao,

455
00:25:49,532 --> 00:25:52,253
do you really want
Zheng Decheng to apologize?

456
00:25:54,052 --> 00:25:56,493
This incident has already damaged

457
00:25:57,013 --> 00:25:58,092
his credibility.

458
00:25:58,772 --> 00:26:00,292
If he apologizes,

459
00:26:00,612 --> 00:26:02,092
will it escalate tensions?

460
00:26:02,812 --> 00:26:03,733
How about this?

461
00:26:04,292 --> 00:26:05,332
First, issue a notice

462
00:26:05,572 --> 00:26:07,532
to clarify the situation.

463
00:26:08,092 --> 00:26:11,013
Reprimand Zheng Decheng internally.

464
00:26:11,332 --> 00:26:12,933
Tone down the incident.

465
00:26:13,253 --> 00:26:14,973
How can we tone down this?

466
00:26:15,812 --> 00:26:18,532
Guan, the cadres are so furious.

467
00:26:18,852 --> 00:26:19,893
As county leaders,

468
00:26:20,213 --> 00:26:21,893
we must make Zheng Decheng step forward.

469
00:26:22,493 --> 00:26:24,973
He owes them
an explanation and accountability.

470
00:26:28,292 --> 00:26:30,253
This situation has escalated

471
00:26:30,413 --> 00:26:32,812
beyond what a simple notice can resolve.

472
00:26:33,493 --> 00:26:35,973
The cadres' frustrations must be vented.

473
00:26:36,693 --> 00:26:37,233
Otherwise,

474
00:26:37,784 --> 00:26:40,024
the pressure on the management
of Yuehai will be greater.

475
00:26:40,493 --> 00:26:42,168
The one who tied the bell must untie it.

476
00:26:42,612 --> 00:26:44,052
Why am I demanding his apology?

477
00:26:44,372 --> 00:26:46,493
To relieve his own burden first,

478
00:26:47,653 --> 00:26:49,332
teach him a lesson,

479
00:26:49,812 --> 00:26:52,812
and make him realize
the consequences of acting recklessly.

480
00:26:54,213 --> 00:26:54,733
Power's back!

481
00:26:57,612 --> 00:26:58,132
Power's back!

482
00:26:59,013 --> 00:26:59,693
Power's back!

