550
00:30:12,013 --> 00:30:12,973
54 yuan and 62 fen.

551
00:30:14,733 --> 00:30:16,013
You remember it quite clearly.

552
00:30:16,653 --> 00:30:17,253
That's all?

553
00:30:17,532 --> 00:30:18,092
Nothing left.

554
00:30:18,413 --> 00:30:19,173
Is that the truth?

555
00:30:19,372 --> 00:30:20,292
Then I'll swear it.

556
00:30:24,532 --> 00:30:27,213
