I won't tolerate that.

557
00:30:27,612 --> 00:30:28,733
Decheng! Decheng!

558
00:30:29,532 --> 00:30:30,453
You can scold your kid.

559
00:30:30,453 --> 00:30:31,612
But you can't hit him.

560
00:30:31,653 --> 00:30:35,132
It's my principle.
Or I can't explain it to my sister.

561
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:41,816
(Dear county committee leaders,)

562
00:30:45,752 --> 00:30:47,544
(I was wrong.)

563
00:31:19,852 --> 00:31:22,040
Personally, I believe
there's only one path now.

564
00:31:22,328 --> 00:31:24,253
Return Binhai Road project
to save the Secretary.

565
00:31:24,413 --> 00:31:25,292
I think we can return.

566
00:31:25,572 --> 00:31:26,132
Exactly.

567
00:31:26,372 --> 00:31:27,256
It must be returned.

568
00:31:27,372 --> 00:31:27,812
Right.

569
00:31:27,893 --> 00:31:30,132
If Ms. Chang backs out,
we'll find other solutions.

570
00:31:30,173 --> 00:31:31,292
Can't we find someone else?

571
00:31:31,292 --> 00:31:32,013
Ms. Gao, you...

572
00:31:32,013 --> 00:31:32,893
Just stop talking.

573
00:31:33,493 --> 00:31:35,693
You know exactly
what happened here, don't you?

574
00:31:36,052 --> 00:31:37,413
Stop. Just reflect on ourselves.

575
00:31:37,893 --> 00:31:39,893
Right? We all understand.
Let's just reflect.

576
00:31:40,173 --> 00:31:41,693
It's already happened. Let's think

577
00:31:41,693 --> 00:31:43,372
about how we can help
the Secretary, right?

578
00:31:43,453 --> 00:31:44,453
Let's go to the county

579
00:31:44,733 --> 00:31:46,453
and support the Secretary tomorrow.

580
00:31:46,612 --> 00:31:47,453
I'll go with you.

581
00:31:47,653 --> 00:31:48,493
Why are you going?

582
00:31:48,852 --> 00:31:49,572
You shouldn't go!

583
00:31:49,572 --> 00:31:52,092
The Secretary ended
up like this for our sake.

584
00:31:52,253 --> 00:31:53,132
We can't abandon him!

585
00:31:53,132 --> 00:31:55,092
Exactly! What would it mean
if we didn't go?

586
00:31:55,092 --> 00:31:56,453
So what other options do we have?

587
00:31:56,973 --> 00:31:57,413
Right.

588
00:31:57,413 --> 00:31:58,292
We'll all go together.

589
00:31:58,413 --> 00:32:00,253
Hear that? They're very emotional.

590
00:32:01,292 --> 00:32:03,453
I originally wanted to make a decision.

591
00:32:03,733 --> 00:32:04,933
But I'm the deputy mayor.

592
00:32:06,493 --> 00:32:08,733
Then let them in. I'll talk to them.

593
00:32:08,973 --> 00:32:09,812
I will let them in.

594
00:32:12,092 --> 00:32:12,772
Stop arguing!

595
00:32:12,772 --> 00:32:13,973
Come in. Come on. Get inside.

596
00:32:14,332 --> 00:32:15,372
Ms. Li will speak.

597
00:32:15,372 --> 00:32:15,973
Come on.

598
00:32:16,052 --> 00:32:16,572
Let's go.

599
00:32:16,933 --> 00:32:17,453
Great!

600
00:32:18,253 --> 00:32:19,512
Listen, I'll remember you.

601
00:32:19,763 --> 00:32:20,893
Didn't you go search before?

602
00:32:20,893 --> 00:32:22,052
Enough. Get down to business.

603
00:32:22,052 --> 00:32:22,372
Ms. Li.

604
00:32:22,372 --> 00:32:22,933
Come on.

605
00:32:22,933 --> 00:32:23,493
Come here.

606
00:32:23,493 --> 00:32:23,896
Ms. Li.

607
00:32:23,896 --> 00:32:24,812
Find a spot to stand.

608
00:32:25,092 --> 00:32:25,893
Stand over there.

609
00:32:26,013 --> 00:32:26,893
Everyone, quiet now!

610
00:32:27,013 --> 00:32:28,132
Raise your hand to ask.

611
00:32:28,213 --> 00:32:28,772
Okay, okay.

612
00:32:29,173 --> 00:32:29,772
- Alright.
- Okay.

613
00:32:29,772 --> 00:32:30,973
Come on, Ms. Li. Please speak.

614
00:32:31,693 --> 00:32:32,532
I'll say a few words.

615
00:32:33,453 --> 00:32:34,092
Two things.

616
00:32:34,453 --> 00:32:36,472
First, tomorrow, no one

617
00:32:36,632 --> 00:32:37,973
goes to the county except me.

618
00:32:38,413 --> 00:32:38,893
Why?

619
00:32:38,893 --> 00:32:39,372
Wait.

620
00:32:39,372 --> 00:32:41,292
If all of you swarm down there,

621
00:32:41,493 --> 00:32:43,772
you'll put immense pressure
on county leaders.

622
00:32:44,413 --> 00:32:47,608
How could they make a decision?
Have you considered the consequences?

623
00:32:48,052 --> 00:32:48,893
What was I saying?

624
00:32:49,132 --> 00:32:50,493
Raise hands! Raise hands to speak.

625
00:32:51,372 --> 00:32:51,733
Don't...

626
00:32:51,733 --> 00:32:52,413
Okay, I...

627
00:32:52,532 --> 00:32:53,372
I think

628
00:32:53,693 --> 00:32:54,744
we should create

629
00:32:55,096 --> 00:32:56,733
some pressure for them, right?

630
00:32:56,733 --> 00:32:57,413
So we could...

631
00:32:57,532 --> 00:32:58,973
I mean, I should go with you.

632
00:33:00,493 --> 00:33:01,052
Good idea.

633
00:33:01,132 --> 00:33:02,372
No, absolutely not.

634
00:33:02,493 --> 00:33:03,052
Go on.

635
00:33:03,213 --> 00:33:05,253
I realize my suggestion also has issues.

636
00:33:05,772 --> 00:33:07,572
Mr. Zheng is fighting
on the front lines.

637
00:33:08,253 --> 00:33:10,372
We can't hold him back.

638
00:33:10,973 --> 00:33:12,024
We just got power back.

639
00:33:12,888 --> 00:33:14,372
There's still much work to be done.

640
00:33:15,253 --> 00:33:15,733
Right?

641
00:33:16,372 --> 00:33:18,413
Second, who said we needed
to return Binhai Road?

642
00:33:18,812 --> 00:33:19,893
- I did.
- We all said.

643
00:33:19,933 --> 00:33:20,733
Yeah, and me too.

644
00:33:21,812 --> 00:33:23,128
This isn't child's play.

645
00:33:23,544 --> 00:33:25,092
Binhai Road gets returned so easily?

646
00:33:25,292 --> 00:33:25,653
Then...

647
00:33:25,653 --> 00:33:28,052
Printing Street must
seize the market opportunity.

648
00:33:28,493 --> 00:33:29,933
We cannot back down on this road.

649
00:33:30,213 --> 00:33:32,056
Moreover, we should build it up

650
00:33:32,443 --> 00:33:33,253
as soon as possible.

651
00:33:35,292 --> 00:33:37,532
I know you all want to help Mr. Zheng.

652
00:33:37,973 --> 00:33:38,532
But

653
00:33:39,052 --> 00:33:40,173
since Mr. Zheng and I

654
00:33:40,213 --> 00:33:42,772
handed Binhai Road over to you,

655
00:33:43,532 --> 00:33:45,372
we had already anticipated
the worst outcome.

656
00:33:46,973 --> 00:33:48,612
Now Mr. Zheng alone

657
00:33:48,772 --> 00:33:50,332
bears all the responsibility.

658
00:33:51,733 --> 00:33:53,893
Before I returned, he instructed me

659
00:33:54,292 --> 00:33:55,332
to ensure production

660
00:33:55,933 --> 00:33:58,413
and also Yuehai's stable progress.

661
00:33:59,292 --> 00:34:01,092
We can't let him down.

662
00:34:02,052 --> 00:34:03,013
We... We got it.

663
00:34:03,733 --> 00:34:04,253
Yes, got it.

664
00:34:04,772 --> 00:34:06,733
Oh, right. And Xingfu Road too.

665
00:34:06,933 --> 00:34:07,572
Mr. Lin,

666
00:34:08,052 --> 00:34:10,813
under no circumstances should we
delay the construction schedule.

667
00:34:11,252 --> 00:34:12,652
Got it. I've got it under control.

668
00:34:13,893 --> 00:34:14,893
Well...

669
00:34:15,172 --> 00:34:16,773
Ms. Li, I have another question.

670
00:34:17,132 --> 00:34:17,933
Tomorrow,

671
00:34:18,132 --> 00:34:20,413
Mr. Zheng won't really
get dismissed, will he?

672
00:34:20,612 --> 00:34:21,092
Yeah.

673
00:34:21,252 --> 00:34:22,652
Will he actually be removed?

674
00:34:23,413 --> 00:34:25,572
- No way.
- I wanted to ask that too.

675
00:34:25,612 --> 00:34:27,212
- This is everyone's...
- Will he?

676
00:34:27,252 --> 00:34:27,960
He won't, right?

677
00:34:28,973 --> 00:34:29,652
Right.

678
00:34:30,493 --> 00:34:31,813
I trust Mr. Zheng.

679
00:34:32,453 --> 00:34:35,333
And I trust our leaders and cadres too.

680
00:34:36,732 --> 00:34:37,624
Get two dough sticks and head to work.

681
00:34:44,152 --> 00:34:45,413
Get them before going to work.

682
00:34:45,413 --> 00:34:46,853
Tie up yesterday's loose ends.

683
00:34:47,222 --> 00:34:47,612
Okay.

684
00:34:47,612 --> 00:34:48,853
Sir, what's wrong?

685
00:34:49,413 --> 00:34:51,252
Is something wrong
with the bun? Not tasty?

686
00:34:55,132 --> 00:34:55,532
No.

687
00:34:57,132 --> 00:34:58,973
Not sure why, but I have no appetite.

688
00:34:59,813 --> 00:35:00,532
Do you have tea?

689
00:35:00,973 --> 00:35:01,853
Yes.

690
00:35:11,132 --> 00:35:12,813
It's quite lively today.

691
00:35:13,652 --> 00:35:15,252
I heard some fool

692
00:35:15,773 --> 00:35:18,373
offended thousands
of cadres county-wide.

693
00:35:19,572 --> 00:35:22,092
So today, he's apologizing
to all county cadres.

694
00:35:24,293 --> 00:35:24,933
I know.

695
00:35:26,572 --> 00:35:27,773
That fool is me.

696
00:35:56,692 --> 00:35:57,413
What's going on?

697
00:35:58,052 --> 00:35:59,493
I didn't eat much this morning.

698
00:36:09,252 --> 00:36:09,933
Mr. Zheng.

699
00:36:11,853 --> 00:36:13,052
Is your apology letter ready?

700
00:36:16,773 --> 00:36:17,933
Of course not.

701
00:36:18,572 --> 00:36:20,252
I couldn't squeeze out a word all night.

702
00:36:20,893 --> 00:36:21,732
Why are you here?

703
00:36:24,052 --> 00:36:26,813
Ms. Li said you're not here
to apologize today.

704
00:36:27,052 --> 00:36:27,933
You're here to fight.

705
00:36:29,413 --> 00:36:31,172
Ms. Li was worried, so she brought me.

706
00:36:35,813 --> 00:36:36,692
How's the town?

707
00:36:37,413 --> 00:36:38,293
Is everyone okay?

708
00:36:38,572 --> 00:36:39,800
Don't worry, power's restored.

709
00:36:40,132 --> 00:36:41,652
Factories are back to production.

710
00:36:41,893 --> 00:36:44,172
Mr. Lin's Xingfu Road project
is proceeding normally.

711
00:36:44,572 --> 00:36:45,212
That's good.

712
00:36:46,973 --> 00:36:48,376
Tiger balm. It refreshes your mind.

713
00:36:48,568 --> 00:36:49,532
This should help you.

714
00:36:57,572 --> 00:36:59,453
Mr. Zheng, open your mouth.

715
00:37:01,092 --> 00:37:02,252
Wh... What is it?

716
00:37:02,453 --> 00:37:03,652
Licorice tablets for throat.

717
00:37:03,933 --> 00:37:04,373
I...

718
00:37:07,773 --> 00:37:08,973
You want me to swallow it dry?

719
00:37:21,453 --> 00:37:22,252
Open your mouth.

720
00:37:24,252 --> 00:37:24,893
What is it?

721
00:37:25,252 --> 00:37:26,172
Tranquilizing tablets.

722
00:37:27,453 --> 00:37:28,440
Tranquilizing tablets.

723
00:37:28,532 --> 00:37:30,333
They relieve tension and help you relax.

724
00:37:30,652 --> 00:37:32,984
Pure herbal ingredients,
without side effects. Don't worry.

725
00:37:34,172 --> 00:37:35,013
Swallow it.

726
00:37:44,092 --> 00:37:45,572
Mr. Zheng, take off your clothes.

727
00:37:45,773 --> 00:37:46,853
Are you crazy?

728
00:37:47,052 --> 00:37:48,013
We're in public!

729
00:37:48,413 --> 00:37:49,373
Don't be nervous.

730
00:37:49,773 --> 00:37:51,132
Enough! Who's nervous?

731
00:37:51,293 --> 00:37:53,172
I wasn't nervous
until you made me nervous.

732
00:37:53,373 --> 00:37:54,333
Stop. Let it be.

733
00:38:00,532 --> 00:38:01,172
Take this.

734
00:38:01,532 --> 00:38:02,652
Who takes this many?

735
00:38:02,732 --> 00:38:03,773
Are you refining elixirs?

736
00:38:03,853 --> 00:38:05,052
You've got me nervous too.

737
00:38:05,532 --> 00:38:06,893
Don't be nervous. It's fine.

738
00:38:07,773 --> 00:38:10,052
Take these
quick-acting heart relief pills.

739
00:38:10,252 --> 00:38:12,853
Take one if you feel short
of breath later

740
00:38:13,333 --> 00:38:14,200
- when you are on stage.
- Take this.

741
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:14,933
This will help.

742
00:38:14,933 --> 00:38:15,933
Yes, take it.

743
00:38:21,453 --> 00:38:23,013
You can do it. You can.

744
00:38:23,453 --> 00:38:24,973
That scared me to death!

745
00:38:25,293 --> 00:38:26,813
It's fine. No problem.

746
00:38:50,252 --> 00:38:51,572
He has no sense of time.

747
00:38:51,933 --> 00:38:54,003
Today, all the cadres and their families

748
00:38:54,424 --> 00:38:55,252
are here.

749
00:38:55,373 --> 00:38:57,612
Let's see how Zheng Decheng
explains this to everyone.

750
00:38:57,720 --> 00:38:59,692
(Auditorium)

751
00:38:59,692 --> 00:39:00,333
Mr. Zheng,

752
00:39:01,453 --> 00:39:03,052
I knew you couldn't draft a speech.

753
00:39:03,493 --> 00:39:04,052
So

754
00:39:04,773 --> 00:39:06,853
when you don't know what to say,
just read this.

755
00:39:06,973 --> 00:39:07,893
It'll help.

756
00:39:12,692 --> 00:39:13,532
Das Kapital?

757
00:39:14,732 --> 00:39:15,453
Will it work?

758
00:39:16,413 --> 00:39:18,613
Mr. Zheng, Mr. Zhao is waiting
for you inside.

759
00:39:18,872 --> 00:39:19,453
Hurry up.

760
00:39:19,572 --> 00:39:20,052
Okay, okay.

761
00:39:20,212 --> 00:39:20,652
Hurry.

762
00:39:21,528 --> 00:39:23,000
(Auditorium)

763
00:39:23,612 --> 00:39:25,013
Make way.

764
00:39:26,532 --> 00:39:27,252
Make way.

765
00:39:27,252 --> 00:39:28,013
- He's here.
- Excuse me.

766
00:39:28,013 --> 00:39:28,612
Coming through.

767
00:39:29,612 --> 00:39:30,293
Let me through.

768
00:39:30,973 --> 00:39:31,893
You wait here for me.

769
00:39:32,052 --> 00:39:32,692
Alright.

770
00:39:39,172 --> 00:39:40,092
Let's see what he says.

771
00:39:58,453 --> 00:39:59,013
Everyone.

772
00:39:59,973 --> 00:40:02,413
Recently, the Yuehai Binhai Road issue

773
00:40:03,212 --> 00:40:04,472
has made Pingchuan County

774
00:40:04,472 --> 00:40:06,373
Committee Compound unsettled.

775
00:40:07,052 --> 00:40:08,172
Regarding the causes

776
00:40:08,252 --> 00:40:10,413
and consequences of this matter,

777
00:40:10,773 --> 00:40:13,052
let's invite Zheng Decheng,

778
00:40:13,293 --> 00:40:15,413
Secretary of Yuehai,
to report in detail.

779
00:40:18,413 --> 00:40:19,092
Make it good.

780
00:40:30,333 --> 00:40:32,853
Mr. Zheng is so pitiful. What can he do?

781
00:40:33,773 --> 00:40:35,333
My heart is pounding.

782
00:40:37,092 --> 00:40:38,212
(Meng was right.)

783
00:40:39,333 --> 00:40:40,933
(It's hard for us now to imagine)

784
00:40:41,692 --> 00:40:43,212
(in such an innocent era,)

785
00:40:44,132 --> 00:40:46,252
(how one person openly apologizing
to thousands)

786
00:40:46,612 --> 00:40:48,052
(must have felt.)

787
00:40:49,933 --> 00:40:51,532
(And most of them)

788
00:40:52,013 --> 00:40:54,652
(were cadres higher in rank
and position than himself.)

789
00:40:56,773 --> 00:40:58,104
(I'm not sure if Zheng Decheng)

790
00:40:58,456 --> 00:40:59,933
(could actually speak.)

791
00:41:28,373 --> 00:41:29,732
Zheng Decheng ran away.

792
00:41:29,732 --> 00:41:30,616
Why did he run away?

793
00:41:30,813 --> 00:41:32,333
- Why did Zheng Decheng run away?
- What's he doing?

794
00:41:37,692 --> 00:41:38,373
What's going on?

795
00:41:39,612 --> 00:41:40,572
Where did he go?

796
00:41:49,652 --> 00:41:50,212
Water.

797
00:41:54,853 --> 00:41:56,333
Slow down. Don't choke!

798
00:41:56,732 --> 00:41:57,813
Just take it all up.

799
00:42:30,453 --> 00:42:31,293
Hello, everyone.

800
00:42:32,732 --> 00:42:34,293
I am the man known as

801
00:42:34,893 --> 00:42:36,413
Pingchuan County's biggest fool,

802
00:42:37,293 --> 00:42:37,973
Zheng Decheng.

803
00:42:42,132 --> 00:42:42,853
You heard him?

804
00:42:43,052 --> 00:42:45,293
Mr. Zheng said he's
Pingchuan County's biggest fool.

805
00:42:46,493 --> 00:42:47,453
- First,
- I heard.

806
00:42:47,692 --> 00:42:49,612
I want to apologize

807
00:42:49,732 --> 00:42:51,896
to all cadres and families
who came to build

808
00:42:52,568 --> 00:42:53,172
in Yuehai.

809
00:42:53,773 --> 00:42:55,652
My personal mistake

810
00:42:56,732 --> 00:42:57,692
has caused you hardship.

811
00:42:59,373 --> 00:42:59,933
I'm sorry.

812
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:10,990
♪Gently holding your face♪

813
00:43:13,340 --> 00:43:18,588
♪To dry the tears from your eyes♪

814
00:43:20,148 --> 00:43:25,341
♪My heart will always be yours♪

815
00:43:27,156 --> 00:43:32,492
♪Tell me you'll never be alone again♪

816
00:43:34,120 --> 00:43:38,108
♪Gazing deep into your eyes♪

817
00:43:41,028 --> 00:43:46,397
♪No further words are needed♪

818
00:43:48,033 --> 00:43:53,238
♪Tightly holding your hand♪

819
00:43:54,972 --> 00:44:00,332
♪The warmth has never changed♪

820
00:44:01,448 --> 00:44:04,556
♪We share the joy♪

821
00:44:04,884 --> 00:44:08,108
♪We share the pain♪

822
00:44:08,362 --> 00:44:13,933
♪We hold the same hope deep inside♪

823
00:44:15,373 --> 00:44:18,372
♪We brave the storm♪

824
00:44:18,892 --> 00:44:21,884
♪We share the quest♪

825
00:44:22,325 --> 00:44:28,268
♪We cherish this love we share♪

826
00:44:31,458 --> 00:44:36,514
♪Whether we've ever met before♪

827
00:44:38,419 --> 00:44:43,829
♪Be it near or far away♪

828
00:44:45,420 --> 00:44:50,603
♪My heartfelt wish for you♪

829
00:44:52,387 --> 00:44:57,517
♪Is for your peace and happiness♪

830
00:44:58,824 --> 00:45:01,994
♪We share the joy♪

831
00:45:02,252 --> 00:45:05,320
♪We share the pain♪

832
00:45:05,744 --> 00:45:11,967
♪We hold the same hope deep inside♪

833
00:45:12,567 --> 00:45:15,630
♪We brave the storm♪

834
00:45:15,966 --> 00:45:19,054
